DQModel

Class DQModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • DQModel.DQModel

  • public class DQModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Makes easier the model construction. If models are loaded from file, this class distinguish the extension. If URI and Endpoint are specified, returns the model or an exception.
    Author:
    Raúl Reguillo Carmona
